[32m+[m[32m声明人(签名):[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m>0/4年//月%日[m
[32m+[m[32m摘要[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m在互联网走进世界每一个角落的今天,互联网信息在不断地膨胀,每日互[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m联网将产生大量的数据,其中涵盖了每天发生发展的各种各样的事件,可谓覆[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m盖人们生产生活的方方面面,这其中包含了大量富有价值的数据,同时又有绝[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m大部分我们不关心的数据,如何从如此海量的信息中抽取有价值的数据,是我[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m们急需思考的问题。[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m系统使用蜘蛛爬虫技术,结合实际需求 发互联网采集系统,使用定向釆[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m集思想,快速定位釆集符合业务需求的互联网数据,然后将釆集结果数据通过[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m文本聚类,归类出符合特性条件的数据集合,以方便后续其他业务的数据支持。[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m本系统釆用java语言面向对象的思想,lucene搜索引擎技术做底层数据检索支[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m持,开源的中文分词器IK,应用方面实现SSH经典Web开发框架,展现一个[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m简单的互联网信息采集分类系统。[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m系统能够为有互联网数据分析需求的个人、企业或者政府提供需求数据的[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m先期过滤聚类,为各种复杂业务的数据分析提供一期标准化数据,在当今这个[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m数据时代里,能发挥很好的作用。[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m关键词:信息采集;网络爬虫;Lucene[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mI[m
[32m+[m[32mAbstract[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mWith the development of internet, the online data grows at high speed every day,[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mincluding all kinds of news, pictures, videos,covering all aspects of human life and[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mbecoming more valuable for users. Hence, how to extract useful information from[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mmassive date for fully using is becoming an extremely urgent question.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mThis dissertation discusses the use of spider crawler technology and develops an[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32minformation collection system focusing on actual demands. The system is based on[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mdirectional collection methods with quick positioning scheme through Web. It aims[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mto meet business requirements, and then cluster the results of text collection for[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mfurther consideration of business.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mIn order to facilitate the data support of the follow-up of other business, the[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32msystem applies JAVA language and Lucene Search Technology. Chinese division[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mmachine IK is the underlying data retrieval support. All is aimed to construct a[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32msimple net information collection classification system.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mThe system provides prefiltering and date clustering for individuals, companies[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mand governments that need internet date analysis. It also provides a standardized date[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mto cope with a variety of complex bussiness date analysis. In this date age, the[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32msysterm can play a very important role.[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32mKey words: Information Collection; Web Crawler; Lucene[m
[32m+[m
